==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chain pump
<hw>Chain" pump`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A pump consisting of an endless
chain, running over a drum or wheel by which it is moved, and dipping
below the water to be raised. The chain has at intervals disks or lifts
which fit the tube through which the ascending part passes and carry the
water to the point of discharge.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>chains</ent>⟦br⟧
